Description: ACP-Calendar
        =============================
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/acp-calendar.png
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/acp-calendar
        
        
        .. image:: https://api.travis-ci.org/luiscberrocal/django-acp-calendar.svg?branch=master
